CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1951, pg. 32 reads: "More Teachers And Attendant To Senior Queen - Left photo: Ernest A. Huddle, Russell C. Phillips and William J. Gaskins won degrees from the School of Education... All are from Pitt."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of University of Pittsburgh graduates, from left: Ernest A. Huddle, Russell C. Phillips, and William J. Gaskins, standing in Syria Mosque, Oakland
